OL,3,CFirearms officer tells inquest he had
OL,4,C'no choice' but to shoot knifeman
OL,6,FA firearms officer who fatally shot a
OL,7,Fman who was brandishing a knife
OL,8,Foutside a police station told an
OL,9,Finquest that he was "left with no
OL,10,Fchoice".
OL,12,FA jury was told that an officer,
OL,13,Freferred to in court as Officer A,
OL,14,Fshot Marius Ciolac with a police
OL,15,Ffirearm in the car park of Ascot Drive
OL,16,FPolice Station in Derby on October 7
OL,17,F2022 after he entered the compound
OL,18,Fholding a blade and a cat in a pet
OL,19,Fcarrier bag.
