OL,3,CFirearms officer tells inquest he had
OL,4,C'no choice' but to shoot knifeman
OL,6,FDerby Coroner's Court heard the
OL,7,Fofficer fired the gun between 18 and
OL,8,F22 seconds after he entered the car
OL,9,Fpark with another armed officer,
OL,10,Fcalled Officer B.
OL,12,FThe identity of both officers is
OL,13,Fprotected by an anonymity order.
OL,15,FThe officer said he told Mr Ciolac to
OL,16,Fdrop the knife, but did not say he was
OL,17,Farmed police, before he ran at him
OL,18,Fwith the weapon raised.
