OL,3,CFirearms officer tells inquest he had
OL,4,C'no choice' but to shoot knifeman
OL,6,FMr Ciolac, a 35-year-old builder who
OL,7,Fwas originally from Romania, smashed
OL,8,Fthrough the first layer of the
OL,9,Fstation's double glazed windows with
OL,10,Fthe knife, appeared to "lick" the
OL,11,Fblade at officers through the door,
OL,12,Fand hit police cars before the two
OL,13,Farmed officers arrived, the court
OL,14,Fheard.
OL,16,FOfficer A told assistant coroner
OL,17,FSabyta Kaushal that he did not hear
OL,18,Finformation passed through the police
OL,19,Fradio about Mr Ciolac's behaviour
OL,20,Fbefore they arrived at the scene.
