OL,3,CFirearms officer tells inquest he had
OL,4,C'no choice' but to shoot knifeman
OL,6,FHe told the court: 'We have not been
OL,7,Fpassed, or I have not heard, that he
OL,8,Fhas smashed through a window, that he
OL,9,Fhas been towards officers at the other
OL,10,Fgate.
OL,12,F'The only information I had when I
OL,13,Farrived on the scene was the sight of
OL,14,Fhim walking towards police officers
OL,15,Fwith a knife.
