OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F371A1738606700
OL,3,CFirearms officer tells inquest he had
OL,4,C'no choice' but to shoot knifeman
OL,6,F'That is the last resort you go to `
OL,7,Fthat is taught to you from day one.'
OL,9,FMr Ciolac's brother and sister, who
OL,10,Fattended the hearing remotely with a
OL,11,FRomanian interpreter, asked Officer A
OL,12,Fabout why he did not shout 'armed
OL,13,Fpolice' before he fired the gun.
OL,15,FHis relatives said: 'We have no
OL,16,Fexperience with the police. We find it
OL,17,Fhard to believe every member of the
OL,18,Fpublic in the country would know what
OL,19,Farmed police look like.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
